     732           5 :     ASSERT_EQ(cs->axisList().size(), 3U);

     736             :

     739           4 :     EXPECT_EQ(cs->axisList()[1]->direction(), AxisDirection::EAST);
     740             : 
     741           4 :     EXPECT_EQ(cs->axisList()[2]->nameStr(), "Ellipsoidal height");

     744             :

     750           3 :     EXPECT_EQ(ellipsoid->semiMajorAxis().unit(), UnitOfMeasure::METRE);
     751           4 :     EXPECT_EQ(ellipsoid->inverseFlattening()->value(), 298.257223563);
